{"tid":2441784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透﹕聯合國再擬聲明譴責暴力對待緬甸示威者　中俄反對譴責軍方政變","createTime":"2021-03-11T02:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T11:48:53.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"02f632418c31e4ac5519e010c853724077353dc4","tid":2441784,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0b808e64cd7ccd95010050c3cb3f72d3_dfOTE_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0b808e64cd7ccd95010050c3cb3f72d3_dfOTE_1200x0.jpg&h=6c3eae5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n修女 Ann Roza Nu 上月底曾於街頭下跪，要求軍人停止行動。圖片來源twitter@Cardinal Charles Bo<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n外媒報道，聯合國安全理事會將發聲明，譴責針對緬甸示威者的暴力。然而聲明沒譴責軍方政變，也沒提出可能有進一步行動。《路透社》指，原因是受到中國、俄羅斯、印度和越南反對。<br />\n<br />\n今次是安理會第二次就緬甸政變發聲明。前一次是在 2 月 4 日，該聲明亦無譴責軍方政變。當時早有傳媒報道，原因同樣為遭到中國與俄羅斯阻撓。事件後來引起緬甸國內外公眾懷疑，中國默許緬甸政變。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/路透-聯合國再擬聲明譴責暴力對待緬甸示威者-中俄反對譴責軍方政變/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F-%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%8D%E6%93%AC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%B0%8D%E5%BE%85%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%84%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A%2F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=9dbe283d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F-%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%8D%E6%93%AC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%B0%8D%E5%BE%85%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%84%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A%2F&h=e6b9939d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/路透-聯合國再擬聲明譴責暴力對待緬甸示威者-中俄反對譴